#: ../../../source/docs/debugging/Sanitizers.rst:314
msgid ""
"This option is fairly expensive because it converts stack allocations into "
"heap allocations, and these allocations are not reused so that future "
"accesses can cause traps. Hence, it is not enabled by default."
msgstr ""

